    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "International Flag Service\nSake\nMenu\nSherry\nManhattan\nMartini\nWhiskey Sour\nGin\nVodka\nRum\nScotch\nBourbon\nCanadian\nAppetizer\nParadise Chicken\nin Oriental Oyster Sauce\nSteamed Rice\n317\nJapanese Honey Cake\nSelected Red or White Wines\nChampagne\nCoffee\n1-2-\nTea.\nSelected Premium Beer\nCigarettes— Assorted Brands\nMints\nCocktails and Liquors $.50\nWine $.50\nBeer and Cigarettes $.30\nChampagne (Split) $1.00\nA suggestion of flags to symbolize all the countries\nserved by Pan American's \"International Flags Service\"\nhas been employed as the theme of this menu cover.\nThe design has been awarded the Certificate of Excellence\nby the American Institute of Graphic Arts, 1970.\n698 JA CC (0181) 1/72\n1997,66.08"
